dc_title_s: Right of Way Plat and Commissioner's Graphic Order - Raster Image File Footprints: Minnesota
dc_description_s: The Right of Way Plat and Commissioner's Graphic Orders footprints layer is a statewide data set. The footprints are constructed from the scanned right of way plat images (raster data) that were georeferenced using the Department of Natural Resource's Control Point Generated Public Land Survey Coverage (vector data), MnDOT's Statewide Basemap (vector data), and other reference data sets as necessary to support the positioning of the images.
dc_creator_sm: Minnesota Department of Transportation, Office of Land Management
